**The Project will be an application that brings together dermanotolgy, laser and skin care clinics in kuwait
in one place, making it easier for pations to search and choose the suitable one for them. The clinics can
advantage of the appointment system provided by the application, products gallery and advertising.**

**The App will content:**
1. Profile for every clinic display information about it and location.
2. Products gallery.
3. Appointment system.
4. Wish and favorite list.
5. advertisements and offers.

 **App functions are:**
 1. Clients can reviews and rating products and clinics.
 2. They can reserve and scheduale appointments.
 3. Advanced search.
 4. sell skin care products.
 
 **Due to the large number of clinics in kuwait and some of them lack for organiz appointments and the marketing
 the application will be useful for both users.**
 
